## Technical Notes

### NWS API Documentation

- **Base URL**: https://api.weather.gov
- **Points Endpoint**: `/points/{latitude},{longitude}`
- **Forecast Endpoint**: URL provided in points response

### CSS Variables (Recommended)

```css
:root {
  --color-primary: #003da5; /* NWS Blue */
  --color-text-primary: #1a1a1a;
  --color-text-secondary: #666666;
  --color-background: #ffffff;
  --font-size-base: 16px;
  --spacing-unit: 8px;
  --transition-duration: 300ms;
}
```

### State Object Example

```javascript
const state = {
  currentOffice: null,
  loadingStatus: 'idle', // 'idle' | 'loading' | 'error' | 'success'
  errorState: null,
  cachedData: {},
  currentForecast: null,
  cacheTimestamp: null,
}
```

