## Success Criteria for Staff-Level Evaluation

✅ **Systems Thinking**: Code structure anticipates scalability and modularity  
✅ **Technical Excellence**: 2-step API, caching, proper error handling  
✅ **UI/UX Excellence**: Professional design, accessibility, responsive  
✅ **Robustness**: Graceful handling of all identified edge cases  
✅ **First Principles**: Demonstrates understanding of the problem domain (weather data, APIs, performance)  
✅ **Attention to Detail**: User-Agent header, null value handling, timezone awareness

---

**Goal**: Deliver a solution that looks and feels like production-ready code while demonstrating deep systems thinking. This is your opportunity to show that you're not just a UI developer, but an engineer who understands the full stack.

